      <talk_answer link_index="n1871_trader_april-1-a" mid="39" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="7"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant April$<BR>As a history buff, I can't miss this opportunity. <FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>, please do me a favour.<BR>Of course, I'm not asking you to do it for free.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1871_trader_april-1-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1871_trader_april-1-b" mid="41" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Okay. What do you want me to do?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="8"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant April$<BR>I heard that the lord of Chiron Island, <FONT color=#a82424>Child Hirendel</FONT>, is a weirdo but has an exquisite taste in landscaping. You can find out about his hobbies if you do me this favour and it would be useful for you too.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1871_trader_april-1-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1871_trader_april-1-c" mid="42" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="9"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant April$<BR>Chiron Island has many unique plants that only grow on that island.<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(April opens a thick book.)</FONT> What I want is a special flower that grows on the island.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1871_trader_april-1-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1871_trader_april-1-d" mid="43" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="10"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant April$<BR>Let me see…. It says <FONT color=#086171>"The petals are white and as big as a coin. It has a blue carpel and the leaves are in rosette form. What is special about this flower is that it has no scent."</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1871_trader_april-1-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1871_trader_april-1-e" mid="45" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>It would be hard to find it since it's so small….</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="11"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant April$<BR>Please get me a flower that matches this description.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1871_trader_april-1-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1871_trader_april-1-f" mid="46" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="12"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant April$<BR>It's not urgent so you can look for it slowly.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1871_trader_april-1-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1871_trader_april-2" mid="57" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="13"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant April$<BR>I heard that it usually grows on the surfaces of monsters living in dark places.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1871_trader_april-2" image="QW_129.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="14"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant April$<BR>So maybe you can get the flower by hunting monsters in a cave.<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Hunt monsters at </FONT><FONT color=#a82424>Secret Seabed Cave</FONT><FONT color=#7e12d2> to get the </FONT><FONT color=#086171>flower</FONT><FONT color=#7e12d2>.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1871_trader_april-3" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1871_trader_april-3-a" mid="47" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Give her the flower)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="15"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant April$<BR>Did you get the flower?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1871_trader_april-3-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1871_trader_april-3-b" mid="48" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>What book is it?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="16"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant April$<BR>Seeing it with my own eyes is better than reading about it a thousand times.<BR>There are only descriptions and no illustrations of some flowers in this book.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1871_trader_april-3-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1871_trader_april-3-c" mid="49" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Wow…….</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="17"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant April$<BR>Oh it's an old book with the meanings of flowers.<BR>Do you know that there used to be Childs who used flowers to send secret messages?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1871_trader_april-3-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1871_trader_april-3-d" mid="50" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="18"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant April$<BR>For example, the meaning of the flower you just got me is <FONT color=#086171>"unwanted visitor"</FONT>.<BR>Sending that flower is like sending a message that there is an intruder or a rival Child is nearby.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1871_trader_april-3-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1871_trader_april-3-e" mid="51" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Are there a lot of flower meanings in Mistland?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="19"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant April$<BR>Instead of sending a letter or communicating verbally, messages could be conveyed using flowers. Isn't it beautiful? It's so unilke the rest of Mistland.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1871_trader_april-3-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1871_trader_april-3-f" mid="52" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="20"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant April$<BR>Yes. But not many people are interested in the meanings that flowers have so they are not that well known. That is probably why they could be used to convey messages secretly.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1871_trader_april-3-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1871_trader_april-3-g" mid="53" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="21"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant April$<BR>But from what I know, many meanings are negative.<BR>Hmm… Let me see….</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
